        <div class="reviewText stacked">
              <span id="reviewTextContainer3090199046" class="readable"
              >
            
<span id="freeTextContainer14221481857118814516">This was my treadmill book for the last few weeks. An amazing account of the middle battles of the Civil War. Mr. Catton’s insights into the army and their leaders were very helpful. The description of the battle at Gettysburg was epic, and the aftermath was enough to make me want to ban war forever. The way this book ended, with President Lincoln getting up to speak at the dedication of the cemetery shows his skills as a writer. Even though we all know what he said, it was the ultimate cliffhan</span>
  <span id="freeText14221481857118814516" style="display:none">This was my treadmill book for the last few weeks. An amazing account of the middle battles of the Civil War. Mr. Catton’s insights into the army and their leaders were very helpful. The description of the battle at Gettysburg was epic, and the aftermath was enough to make me want to ban war forever. The way this book ended, with President Lincoln getting up to speak at the dedication of the cemetery shows his skills as a writer. Even though we all know what he said, it was the ultimate cliffhanger.</span>
  <a data-text-id="14221481857118814516" href="#" onclick="swapContent($(this));; return false;">...more</a>

          </span>
