<div id="review_2780382460" class="review" itemprop="reviews" itemscope itemtype="http://schema.org/Review">
  <link itemprop="url" href="https://www.goodreads.com/review/show/2780382460" />
    <a title="Phillip Mclaughlin" class="left imgcol" href="/user/show/18231455-phillip-mclaughlin"><img alt="Phillip Mclaughlin" src="https://images.gr-assets.com/users/1362916690p2/18231455.jpg" /></a>

  <div class="left bodycol">
    <div class="reviewHeader uitext stacked">
        <a class="reviewDate createdAt right" href="/review/show/2780382460?book_show_action=true">Apr 18, 2019</a>

      <span itemprop="author" itemscope itemtype="http://schema.org/Person">
        <a title="Phillip Mclaughlin" class="user" itemprop="url" name="Phillip Mclaughlin" href="/user/show/18231455-phillip-mclaughlin">Phillip Mclaughlin</a>
      </span>

        rated it
        <span class=" staticStars notranslate" title="it was amazing"><span size="15x15" class="staticStar p10">it was amazing</span><span size="15x15" class="staticStar p10"></span><span size="15x15" class="staticStar p10"></span><span size="15x15" class="staticStar p10"></span><span size="15x15" class="staticStar p10"></span></span>

          <span class="greyText">&nbsp;&middot;&nbsp;</span>
          <a class="lightGreyText" title="Kindle Edition " href="/book/show/27418674-glory-road">review of another edition</a>


        

    </div>


        <div class="reviewText stacked">
              <span id="reviewTextContainer2780382460" class="readable"
              >
            
<span id="freeTextContainer17066996975805194786"><strong>Fredericksburg to Gettysburg a crucial time</strong><br/><br/>I annually reread Bruce Catton’s Army of the Potomac Trilogy. This was the first set of narrative history I encountered just before the Centennial and left an indelible mark on my youth as the benchmark of a journalist writing historical work. Glory Road is truly readable, well researched and just the center of the set. <br/>Highly recommend to old and young.</span>

          </span>
        </div>


      <div class="reviewFooter uitext buttons">
          

